        <li>TODO: Experience with modern web frameworks (React, Next.js, Node.js)</li>
        <li>TODO: Machine learning experience with TensorFlow and PyTorch</li>
        <li>TODO: Cloud infrastructure experience with AWS and Docker</li>
        <li>TODO: Excellent communication and teamwork skills</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
